Just a few logistical notes
before we start our discussion.

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:15.190
I want to let everyone know
that the event is being streamed

00:02:15.190 --> 00:02:17.980
through Facebook Live on the
Emory University website,

00:02:17.980 --> 00:02:20.302
and we're also
