00:50:06.528 --> 00:50:07.570
walking through the book.

00:50:07.570 --> 00:50:09.970
And it was just a
wonderful, amazing book.

00:50:09.970 --> 00:50:12.160
So I would have to say
The Temple of My Familiar

00:50:12.160 --> 00:50:15.460
is one that really
continues to be one

00:50:15.460 --> 00:50:18.400
that I go back to just for the
pleasure of opening to any page

00:50:18.400 --> 00:50:20.458
and saying, oh, I
remember that's the story

00:50:20.458 --> 00:50:21.250
about the feathers.

00:50:21.250 --> 00:50:23.810
Oh, I remember that's the
