00:56:28.437 --> 00:56:30.520
It's kind of like let's
go have dinner and tell me

00:56:30.520 --> 00:56:31.450
how it's going.

00:56:31.450 --> 00:56:35.000
So find somebody that you like
and tell them what you know.

00:56:35.000 --> 00:56:35.500
Fabulous.

00:56:35.500 --> 00:56:36.250
